## What

A demonstration of a few of Azure's Security features including: Access Control (AIM), Just in Time (JIT) access control,
Security Center Recommendations, Virtual Machine Security Recommendations, and Key Vault.

## Outcomes

Knowledge sharing and learning the newer security features of Azure.
